Kasancewar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) da ke tasowa a cikin EU/Turai da Birtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Kasancewar cutar ta Coronavirus (COVID-19) ta karuwa, irin wannan yanayin a cikin kasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila ya nuna cewa ko da yake cutar ta yadu a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban a matakai daban-daban, cutar ta COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar da aka samu daga cutar a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da garuruwan kulawa ta musamman suna bukatar su kara kasancewa a shirye don manyan magungunan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kula da lafiya, musamman kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2020, an samu rahoton wani rukuni na marasa lafiya na cutar sankara da ba a san dalilinsa ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar China ta ba da rahoton cewa cutar ta haifar da wani sabon nau'in coronavirus wanda daga yanzu ake kira cutar ta Coronavirus 2 ta hanyar cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani ko kuma ta hanyar taƙaitaccen SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, rashin lafiyar da aka samu daga kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira shi cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai da aka samu sun nuna cewa kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 suna kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin su sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na al'ummomin, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan cuta wanda ya sa marasa lafiya suka shiga asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na sauran al'ummomin da suka kamu da mummunan cuta suka shiga cikin kulawa ta musamman.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su daga COVID-19 ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/kasashen tattalin arziki na Turai da Ingila, kuma mun kwatanta shi da yanayin a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Muna kuma kwatanta yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila da waɗanda ke kamuwa da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EU da Ingila
Bayan haka, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu yankuna na duniya, kuma halin da cutar ta COVID-19 ke ciki a sauran sassan duniya yana bin irin wannan yanayin a kasar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Sakataren Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya sanar da barkewar cutar COVID-19.
A cikin wata mujallar Eurosurveillance ta 5 ga Maris 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon kamuwa da cutar coronavirus a Turai bisa ga ma'anar Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya.
A cikin EU/Economic Region, an samu kamuwa da cutar ta farko a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a Faransa tsakanin fasinjojin da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano mutane masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen 30 na EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila (UK), wanda ya ba da rahoton kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da kamuwa da cutar 1,727 a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa ƙarshen wannan kwanan wata, inda Italiya kadai ta sami kamuwa da cutar 1,7750 da mutuwar 1,441.
Samun adadi da kuma samun adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana samun lambobin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a kowace ƙasa a kowace rana daga kafofin hukuma kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki a waɗannan ƙasashe da kuma Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, kuma ana sabunta su da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EU da Ingila da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin tushen ƙayyade yaduwar cutar COVID-19, mun ƙayyade tsawon lokacin da aka rage yawan kwanaki 14 na kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, don haka an yi la'akari da lokacin COVID-19 na al'ada, a kowace ƙasa memba na EU / EU da Ingila, a cikin lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
An kuma kwatanta yawan marasa lafiya a kowace ƙasa a cikin jimlar Janairu 31 zuwa Maris 15, 2020, kamar yadda aka nuna a karfe 8:00 na safe na ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasancewar kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU / EU da Ingila
Hanyoyin da aka lura a cikin rage yawan kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EU da Ingila sun dace da yanayin da aka ambata a cikin lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
A cikin duka, a cikin EU / EU da Ingila, an fara samun COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen da ke cikin EU / EU da kuma Ingila a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan kuma a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (abun da aka haɗa).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda yawan adadin marasa lafiya da aka samu daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/Economic Union da Birtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwa a cikin COVID-19 (ƙididdiga sun haɗa).
Shafi na 2 ya kwatanta yawan adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila da waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya bayyana cewa, a karfe 8:00 na safe, 15 ga Maris, wasu kasashe 15 na EU / EU da Birtaniya sun ba da rahoton yawan adadin kamuwa da cutar, wanda ya yi daidai da na Italiya a cikin makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 na ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU / EU da Ingila.
Hanyoyin da aka lura da tarin COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar za ta yadu da irin wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Duk da cewa ƙasashe suna fuskantar matakai daban-daban na yaduwar cutar, akwai bambance-bambance a cikin yadda hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe ke amsawa, kuma a ƙasashe daban-daban, ana amfani da ƙa'idodi daban-daban don mutanen da ke buƙatar yin gwajin tabbatarwa ko ƙarin gwajin COVID-19.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke da cutar ta Italiya sun ba da rahoton halin da ake ciki inda kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa an riga an kammala babban ƙarfin asibitoci da sassan kulawa na musamman a waɗannan yankuna.
A halin yanzu, a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, kashi 6% da 1% na kasashe ne kawai ke da bayanai game da karɓar marasa lafiya COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko shiga cikin kulawa ta musamman (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara su cikin tsari don amfani da su a matsayin ƙarin bayanan kulawa na yanzu kuma a mayar da hankali kan wasu ɓangarorin da aka ruwaito da kuma ɓangarorin mutuwa.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a tsakanin 11 zuwa 2010 ya nuna bambanci mai yawa a cikin samun damar zuwa asibitocin kulawa na musamman da matsakaici a Turai, inda ya bambanta daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal ga kowane 100,000 mutane.
Wannan yana nufin cewa waɗannan ƙasashe suna da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (mafi yawan wuraren kulawa na musamman da matsakaici 12.5 a kowace 100,000 mutane a shekara ta 2011-2010).
An gabatar da yanayin tsarawa dangane da wadatar da damar kiwon lafiya da magani tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU / EU da Burtaniya game da yawan marasa lafiya COVID-19 da ke da haɗarin > 90% fiye da ƙarfin wuraren kula da lafiya na musamman a cikin tsarin ECDC na shida na kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Tun da an riga an lura da cututtukan cututtuka a wasu yankuna a cikin ƙasashen EU / EU da Ingila, kuma asibitoci da wuraren kulawa na musamman suna ba da sabis ga yawan jama'a na yanki, dole ne a ba da bayanai game da cututtuka da wuraren kulawa na musamman a cikin tsari na Ƙungiyoyin Ƙungiyoyi don Matsayi na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar cutar a Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen EU / EU da Ingila.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da kuma wuraren kulawa na musamman su shirya kansu don magance yanayin ci gaba da yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma samar da shirye-shirye don karɓar marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, musamman a cikin wuraren kulawa na musamman, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da aka kamu da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin ƙididdigar haɗarin ECDC na kwanan nan, yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 zuwa hanzari, gaba da yaduwa da kuma daidaitaccen tsarin aiki tare da sauya ra'ayi daga ƙuntatawa zuwa rage saurin annobar, saboda idan ba a ɗauki matakan da suka dace ba, ƙimar da ake tsammani na masu kamuwa da cutar ba za ta sami damar da za a ba hukumomin yanke shawara da asibitoci don ganowa, karɓa da aiwatar da martani mai kyau ba.
Har ila yau, kimantaccen haɗari na sauri ya lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Kasashe suna da ɗan gajeren lokaci don ƙarfafa ƙoƙarin sarrafa su da rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 don haka rage matsin lamba akan tsarin kiwon lafiya da magani.
Idan ba a iya yin haka ba, tsarin kula da lafiya na sauran EU / EU na iya fuskantar babban adadin marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar ta Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar da cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS), ta haifar da mutuwar mutane fiye da 3,000 da kamuwa da cutar fiye da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, kuma a matsayin haka, ta haifar da bala'in ɗan adam.
Hakanan SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama kamar wanda ya haifar da SARS-CoV a cikin dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, wanda ya kamu da cutar ta hanyar kwayoyin halitta, kuma yana haifar da bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya ta hanyar aiwatar da irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da ƙarancin kamuwa da cutar, yana cutar da tsofaffi da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
A cikin martani ga karuwar wallafe-wallafen game da wannan sabon cuta, wannan ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da bincike mai zurfi.
Za mu samar da bayanai na asali game da cututtukan cututtuka, etiology, virology, ganewa, magani, gargadi da rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, ana fatan wannan binciken zai taimaka wajen gano wannan cuta mai haɗari da kuma kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba za a iya mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa da aka nemi su zauna a gida a lokacin hutu da kuma makonni masu yawa bayan barkewar sabuwar cuta ta cutar.
Wannan cutar tana da kamanceceniya da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wanda ya haifar da barkewar cutar ta SARS a shekara ta 2003, saboda haka, a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta zabi sunan SARS-CoV-2 da kuma sunan cutar da ta danganta da ita, CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19) (Covid-19 ko COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a duk faɗin ƙasar da kuma wasu ƙasashe 5 a duniya.
Tun daga ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar ta musamman fiye da 80,000, wanda adadin marasa lafiya da aka sallama ya wuce 40,000, kuma fiye da 3,000 sun mutu.
