Wannan binciken na nazari ne wanda ke nufin sake nazarin ci gaban bincike a sababbin fannoni da ake nema.
A cikin sakin layi na biyu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus da ake kira Middle East respiratory syndrome (wanda ya zama sananne a shekara ta 2012).
Za mu tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafi da kuma gano cutar, da kuma wasu muhimman tambayoyi.
An yi amfani da coronavirus a matsayin mai cutar da ba ta da cutar a cikin mutane kuma sun kasance sun haifar da kusan 15% na sanyi na yau da kullum.
Koyaya, a cikin karni na yanzu, mun haɗu da ƙwayoyin cuta na mutum sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da farkon annobar cutar a cikin 2003 a China da 2012 a Saudiyya, kuma a cikin ɗan gajeren lokaci sun faɗaɗa zuwa wasu ƙasashe, suna haifar da mummunan cututtuka da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annoba ta uku ta coronavirus a tarihin ɗan adam.
