Duk da haka, magance wannan matsalar yana da wuya saboda dogon lokaci da ake buƙata don tsarawa da samar da allurar rigakafi (tsakanin watanni 18) da kuma canjin canjin coronavirus.
A matsayin sabon cuta, COVID-19 kwanan nan ya fara bayyana a cikin dubban marasa lafiya.
