Shekara: Shekara ita ce mafi mahimmancin sanarwa game da cutar SARS, kamar yadda yake a cikin COVID-19.
COVID-19 yana faruwa ne a cikin shekaru 65-30, wanda ya shafi kashi 47.7% na mutanen da suka wuce shekaru 50 a cikin binciken da ya shafi marasa lafiya 8,866, wanda aka bayyana a sama.
Marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa ta musamman sun fi fuskantar cututtukan zuciya da cututtukan baya kuma sun fi tsufa fiye da marasa lafiya da ba su buƙatar kulawa ta musamman (tare da matsakaicin shekaru 66 zuwa 51), kuma wannan yana ba da shawarar cewa ana iya ɗaukar shekaru a matsayin sanarwa na sakamakon marasa lafiya da COVID-19.
Jima'i: Kamar yadda aka ambata a sama, SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza fiye da mata (0.31 cikin 100,000, idan aka kwatanta da 0.27 cikin 100,000).
Cututtuka da cututtuka: Marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman suna da mafi kusantar samun rauni mai tsanani ko bugun zuciya.
Har ila yau, cututtukan zuciya sun kasance babban dalilin mutuwa a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar ta SARS.
An ruwaito cewa SARS-CoV-2 na iya haɗuwa da Clanchocytes na ACE2-mai kyau wanda zai iya haifar da rikicewar hanta a cikin marasa lafiya COVID-19.
Ya kamata a lura cewa shekaru da cututtuka suna da dangantaka mai ƙarfi kuma suna iya yin hulɗa.
Abubuwan da aka gano a dakin gwaje-gwaje ba su da kyau: matakin furotin C mai amsawa a cikin jini yana nuna girman ƙonewa ko lalacewar ƙwayar cuta kuma an ba da shawarar cewa yana da mahimmanci a matsayin mai gano cutar, amsawa ga magani da kuma kyakkyawan farfadowa.
An bayar da shawarar cewa akwai alaƙa tsakanin matakin CRP da tsanani da kuma farkon COVID-19.
Bugu da ƙari, ƙaruwar matakan lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aminotransferase aspartate (AST), aminotransferase alanine (ALT), da kuma creatine kinase (CK) na iya zama tasiri a cikin hasashen sakamakon.
Wadannan enzymes suna bayyana sosai a cikin wasu kayan jiki, musamman a zuciya da hanta, kuma suna saki lokacin da aka lalata kayan.
Saboda haka, suna da alamun gargajiya don gano cututtukan zuciya ko hanta.
Babban alamun asibiti: Don yin hasashen sakamakon da kuma sakamakon COVID-19, dole ne a yi la'akari da radiography na ƙirjin da ci gaban alamun asibiti tare da sauran abubuwan da suka shafi.
