Tun da ake amfani da manyan allurai na corticosteroids a cikin marasa lafiya masu cutar SARS, yawancin waɗanda suka tsira daga ƙarancin jini na ƙarancin ƙwayoyin ƙashi suna fama da rashin ƙarfi na dogon lokaci da rashin ingancin rayuwa.
Saboda haka, idan ya zama dole, ya kamata a yi amfani da steroids a ƙananan sashi kuma a cikin gajeren lokaci ga marasa lafiya COVID-19.
