Wadannan matakan suna da tasiri wajen ragewa da kuma hana yaduwar cutar.
Ko da yake an san cutar SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin sabon cutar da ta fara bayyana a duniya, babban kamanceceniya da SARS-CoV da aka ruwaito a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 ya zama babban gargadi ga China, yana ba da labarin barkewar cutar SARS a shekara ta 2003.
Duk da haka, ba a yi wani ƙoƙari na samar da kwanciyar hankali ba har zuwa 19 ga Janairu, 2020, ranar da shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya sanar da cewa sabon kwayar cutar tana da iyakanceccen ikon watsawa da tasiri ga mutum, kuma yana da damar hana cutar.
Wannan sakon ya sa aka yi watsi da gargadin jama'a, musamman a yayin da kasar ta shirya bikin bikin bazara na sabuwar shekara, kuma ta haka ne ta rasa babbar dama don hana yaduwar cutar a Wuhan.
Cibiyoyin kula da cututtuka a China na iya ɗaukar wannan darasi mai wuya kuma suna yin manyan ci gaba don matakan gaba.
