A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, cibiyar kula da lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurka ta sanar da cewa sun kirkiro kayan gwajin kansu.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta fara gwajin cutar, wanda ya sanya ainihin yaduwar cutar cikin duhu.
Saboda kuskuren gwajin gwaji, wanda gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, saboda rashin amincewa da gwajin gwaji na gwamnati, ta hanyar gwamnatin tarayya (ta hanyar jami'o'i, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa karshen Fabrairu, da kuma ƙuntataccen ƙa'idodin ga mutanen da suka cancanci yin gwaji, gwaje-gwajen da aka yi har zuwa farkon Maris (dokta ta likita ta zama dole) sun zama marasa inganci.
A ranar 27 ga Fabrairu, Washington Post ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwajin gwaji kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
Har zuwa ranar 13 ga Maris, Atlantic ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaji kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, Associated Press ta ruwaito cewa: Mutane da yawa da ke da alamun rashin lafiya da kuma shawarar likita don yin gwaji sun jira na tsawon sa'o'i zuwa kwanaki don yin gwaji. Bayan da aka fara bayar da rahoton mutuwar a Amurka a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, G. Innsley, gwamnan jihar ya sanar da dokar ta baci ta jihar, wani mataki da sauran jihohi suka bi nan da nan.
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun rufe makarantun su a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, ƙungiyar masu ilimin cututtuka a Royal College of London sun ba da tsinkaya game da tasirin coronavirus a Amurka.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan yarjejeniyar bayar da tallafin tallafi da kuma shirye-shirye, wanda ya ba da dala biliyan 8.3 don tallafawa ayyukan tarayya da ake buƙata don amsa cutar.
Kamfanoni sun sanya takunkumin tafiye-tafiye ga ma'aikata, sun soke taron, kuma sun ƙarfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanya takunkumin tafiye-tafiye na kwanaki 30 ga yawancin kasashen Turai, banda Ingila, wanda ya fara aiki daga ranar 13 ga Maris.
Kashegari, ya kafa wasu takunkumi musamman ga Ingila da Ireland.
