Tun daga ranar 15 ga Maris, yawancin kasuwancin Amurka sun rufe ko rage awoyi don rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga Maris, an tabbatar da cutar a duk jihohi 50 da kuma yankin Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ruwaito cewa New York City tana da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus 10,700, wanda ya fi yawan adadin kamuwa da cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga watan Maris, Wally ya bayyana cewa nisan zamantakewa yana da tasiri, saboda ƙididdigar saurin ninka lokuta ya ragu daga kwanaki 2 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga Maris, an tabbatar da cewa akwai mutane 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar a birnin New York City, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu saboda kamuwa da cutar. A ranar 26 ga Maris, an ruwaito cewa Amurka tana da ƙarin kamuwa da cutar fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya. A ranar 8 ga Afrilu, an tabbatar da 4,0335 a Amurka, kuma mutane 12,841 sun rasa rayukansu.
A cewar rahotanni a kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaba Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idodin nisan jama'a har zuwa ranar 30 ga Afrilu.
