Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'i na Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen tura tallafi ga yankunan da ke fama da cutar ta coronavirus a kasar Sin. Kamar dai wata kungiya ta hadin gwiwa a yankin Chicago ta gudanar da aikawa da masks 50,000 na N95 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
