Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba da kokarin da jami'an kasar Sin ke yi na sarrafa cutar.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta kwatanta wannan yanayin da annobar SARS a 2002-2004, lokacin da aka zargi jami'an kasar Sin da ɓoye bayanai, wanda hakan ya shafi kokarin hana yaduwar cutar da kuma rage yaduwar cutar, kuma a halin yanzu, a cikin rikicin da ke faruwa, gwamnatin tarayya ta "yi aiki na yau da kullum don hana barkewar cutar kafin hutun sabuwar shekara ta hasken rana".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, wakilin Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Gooding Gali, a cikin martani ga shawarar da manyan hukumomi suka yanke na aiwatar da haramcin sufuri a Wuhan, ya bayyana cewa, "ba lallai ba ne shawarar Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ce", amma "babban alama ce ta sadaukar da kai ga hana annobar a inda ta fi muni a ko'ina", kuma ya kira ta "ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar a kasashen waje da kuma karuwar adadin mutane a wasu ƙasashe, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin dokar ta baci ta duniya da kuma karo na shida da ta faru tun lokacin da aka fara cutar a lokacin annobar cutar mura ta 2009.
