Anjeocanthin-2B (ACE2) shine enzyme wanda ke haɗe zuwa waje (ƙwayoyin halitta) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, hanci da jini.
ACE2 yana magance aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin 2 da kuma ƙara angiotensin (da 1-7) kuma ya sanya shi kyakkyawan magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 har yanzu yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin kwayoyin halitta ga wasu coronavirus.
An kira wani nau'in na mutum na enzyme hACE2 sau da yawa.
Anjeotancin-2 mai canzawa yana dauke da wani metalanzyme wanda ke dauke da wani abu mai mahimmanci wanda yake a saman kwayoyin ciki da sauran kwayoyin.
Protein ACE2 yana dauke da yankin M2 na ne-terminal peptidease da kuma yankin karɓar ƙananan amino acid cholesterol C-terminal.
ACE2 wani nau'i ne na furotin na gland na nau'i guda daya wanda ke da tasirin enzymatic wanda ke samuwa a saman kwayoyin a cikin huhu da sauran kayan.
Ƙarfin waje na kwayar ACE2 yana ƙunshe da wani enzyme da ake kira shadase na glandular translucent, kuma furotin mai narkewa da aka samu yana fitowa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe yana fitarwa cikin urine.
ACE2 yana samuwa a mafi yawan sassan jiki: ACE2 yana haɗuwa da membrane na ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin cuta na ciki da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jijiyoyin jiki a mafi yawan sassan.
Ana samun ACE2 mRNA a cikin kwakwalwa, tsarin tsarin, hypothalamus, da ƙwaƙwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine aiki a matsayin ACE antibody.
ACE hormone ya raba angiotensin daya zuwa angiotensin biyu, wanda shine mai hana jijiyoyi.
ACE2 a maimakon haka, yana raba aminonin carboxylic-terminal alanyl-alanyl daga angiotensin-du (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana hydrolyzing shi zuwa angiotensin mai faɗaɗa jijiya (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya haifar da rabuwa daga wasu peptides, ciki har da /DS-Arg9)-Bridkinin, Neurotensin, Dinorphine A, da Grelin.
ACE2 yana daidaita wucewar masu ɗaukar amino acid SLC6A19 na tsaka tsaki daga gland, kuma yana taka rawa a cikin cututtukan zuciya.
ACE2 a matsayin furotin na membrane, yana taka rawa a matsayin babban shigarwa zuwa kwayar cutar don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, ciki har da HCoV-NL63 (virus da ke haifar da SARS) da SARS-CoV-2 (virus da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, haɗuwa da furotin S1 na Spike a cikin SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 tare da yankin ACE2 a saman sel, yana haifar da endocytosis da kuma watsa duka ƙwayoyin cuta da enzymes zuwa endosomes a cikin sel.
Wannan tsari na shigarwa yana buƙatar shirya furotin S na TMPRSS2 mai karɓar bakuncin protease, wanda ke da kariya a matsayin magani mai yuwuwa. Wannan ya haifar da zato cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin kwayoyin zai iya taimakawa wajen magance kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da haka, kungiyoyi da yawa da kuma cibiyoyin kulawa sun bada shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE da maganin ARB.
