An gano cewa ACE2 na mutum, nootropic (rhACE2), wani sabon magani ne don mummunan rauni na huhu kuma yana haifar da ingantaccen tsarin hanci da kuma iskar oxygen a cikin aladu da ke fama da cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani na lipopolysaccharide.
